---
title: Chinese Beef & Green Bean Stir-Fry with Roasted Cashews
description: Everyone loves a stir-fry, but when you add a rainbow of crisp veggies, tender beef mince and lots of aromatic flavours, this family favourite will be even more beloved. With a scattering of crunchy cashews and fluffy jasmine rice, there’s a reason this meal is a guaranteed crowd-pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-beef-green-bean-stir-fry-d6e01931.jpg
